# smpl
Simplified plotting and fitting in python.

## Documentation

-   <https://smpl.readthedocs.io/en/stable/>
-   <https://apn-pucky.github.io/smpl/index.html>

## Versions

### Stable

```sh
pip install smpl
```

Optional: --user or --upgrade

### Dev

```sh
pip install --index-url https://test.pypi.org/simple/ smpl
```
